and you're in some other time. We seem too many conjurer's boxes, and it seemed to me unrealistic

19:08.540 --> 19:13.240
if I ever built a box like that and I thought it was going to take me to another time,

19:13.860 --> 19:19.100
I certainly would jump into it and press the button. It would conduct a long series of tests

19:19.100 --> 19:22.120
and experiments first, and none of that here I was ever thinking to do this.

