do that, and so the story was about some physicists who had stumbled upon this phenomenon and had

20:01.800 --> 20:07.560
realized that if what they were seeing meant what they thought it meant, it meant that they could

20:09.860 --> 20:15.040
actually inject information into the past and change the past with all the questions that

20:15.040 --> 20:26.520
implied, and being proceeded to test this phenomenon and the pains and very very strange results.

